Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好过圣诞了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for Christmas, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.91,0:00:22.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:22.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.97,0:00:40.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:40.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.81,0:00:45.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是海绵宝宝圣诞特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:45.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the SpongeBob Christmas Special
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:49.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,232)}海绵宝宝\N圣诞特辑
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是恩斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, direct from Encino
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有请全美最爱的海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,America's favorite pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.20,0:01:00.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,及海绵宝宝粉丝俱乐部的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:01:00.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and president of the SpongeBob SquarePants Fan Club
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,770)}派斯
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.17,0:01:12.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:12.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海盗派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝粉丝俱乐部的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,president of the SpongeBob SquarePants Fan Club
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.98,0:01:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就是圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七大洋里最好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there ain't nothing better in the seven seas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非裤头村的圣诞节莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a Bikini Bottom Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是一年中最神奇的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure is a magical time of year
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝现在肯定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why I'll bet old SpongeBob is gearing up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为迎接圣诞老人做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Santa Claus right now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.21,0:01:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:54.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,704)}欢迎圣诞老人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对无脊椎动物来说还挺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad for a creature with no vertebrae
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看派大星兄弟肯定在做他那份装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure our pal Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is doing his share of the decorating
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也在为圣诞节做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, too, am also preparing for Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没烤的饼干面团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unbaked cookie dough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:22.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1250,998)}面粉
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂想吃饼干面团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty want cookie dough
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.41,0:02:25.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:25.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cookie
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.41,0:02:26.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:26.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.16,0:02:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cookie
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.25,0:02:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cookie
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.87,0:02:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我舔一口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give us a lick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快滚  你个鸡毛掸子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back off, you flying freak
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clarify, please
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这饼干糊是给孩子们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here cookie dough is for the children
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是给烦人鹦鹉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not for pesky parrots
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三声铃声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three bells
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都知道三声铃声什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we all know what three bells means
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you silly livers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人落海了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man overboard?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不理你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, I'm ignoring
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.86,0:02:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,读粉丝来信的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to open fan letters
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我啊你  傻鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, give it, you birdbrain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死鸟别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet, you infernal bird
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这封寄给我们的信是来自
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This letter comes to us from
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已隐藏姓名与地址
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Name and address withheld
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他写道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he writes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dear SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今年十岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I am ten years old
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想知道你是不是跟我一样喜欢圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"and I was wondering if
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you like Christmas as much as I do
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真诚的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sincerely yours"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已隐藏姓名与地址
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Name and address withheld
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这问题问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A very good question
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是你们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you know
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村本来是不过圣诞节的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they didn't always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,celebrate Christmas in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真没过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They didn't?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对的  害我脖子疼的死鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, sir, my fine-feathered little neck pain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.87,0:03:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前有一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There was a time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村里没一个人听说过有圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when no one had even heard of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.92,0:03:57.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想来听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:57.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to hear
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝第一次过圣诞节的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the story of SpongeBob's very first Christmas?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.97,0:04:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我饼干面团都吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ate all me cookie dough
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,节目开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On with the show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:18.44,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(177,349)}什么圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.67\pos(472,402)}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:23.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.67\pos(426,344)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.67\pos(304,466)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.67\pos(328,346)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.67\pos(484,678)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我要偷偷接近过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today I'm going sneak up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.16,0:04:35.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用超级机密空手道招数来偷袭珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:35.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get that Sandy with a super-sneaky karate move
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她这是在搞什么邪恶的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What diabolical act is she committing now?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪快后退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand back, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说没有着火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, I guess there's no fire?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底是哪根筋不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of the Alamo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is wrong with you, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道你从来就没见过圣诞树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't you never seen a Christmas tree before?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么圣诞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas who?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.08,0:05:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连什么是圣诞都没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all never heard of Christmas?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你在德州的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is she a friend from Texas?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然从来没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe y'all haven't heard about
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再多跟我讲点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me more about this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪叙述了橡皮糖和口笛的神奇传说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy wove a magical tale of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gumdrops and penny whistles
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提到了做玩具的精灵和会飞的驯鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She told of toy-making elves and flying reindeer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过最棒的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But best of all
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她还提到了那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she told of the one they call
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,434)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后大家都会假装喜欢水果蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and everyone pretends to like the fruitcake
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈欠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yawn
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过最棒的地方就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the best part is
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以写信给这个叫圣诞老人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can write a letter to this guy Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉他你想要什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and tell him what you want
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.83,0:05:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等他过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when he comes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会把东西给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he brings it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟灯神一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like a genie
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你们旱鸭子在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you lubbers
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过只要有哪个谁白送免费玩意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but any fella who's giving away free stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个谁就会是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a friend o' mine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以开始写信了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can get started on your letter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会真的会有人过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe anybody would celebrate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.06,0:06:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让个潜行犯闯进家里送礼的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a holiday where a jolly prowler breaks into your house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leaves gifts
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟灯神一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like a genie
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pipe down, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to concentrate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西简直就是一张空白支票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This thing's as good as a blank check
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是圣诞老人第一国家银行发行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,direct from the First National Bank of Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  下一个是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, who's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这张纸上没有字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no words on this paper
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然还没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not yet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写字用的棍子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A writing stick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,write a letter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别这么幼稚行不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, grow up, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人会因为我写了封破信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's going to give me a gift
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就给我礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just because I write them a stupid letter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我把纸给撕破了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I ripped my paper
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能再来一张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I have another one?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来写吧  章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.31,0:07:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的圣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dear San"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么又来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.86,0:07:08.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:08.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我写
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,watch me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dear Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是要问我这个圣诞节要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What do I want for Christmas, you may ask?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想要让你来跟裤头村的各位见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"All I want is for you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to visit the gentle folk here in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is my wish"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特别设计了这个装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I designed this mechanism specifically
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把瓶子发射到海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to shoot bottles to the surface
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人的希望就寄托在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hopes of everyone rests on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这瓶子的成功首航上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the success of its maiden voyage
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire in the hole
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Santa?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他得等平安夜才会来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't come till Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my demands
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean letter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你许愿要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you wish for?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pony
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身上驮着满满几袋子的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With saddle bags full of money
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你许愿要什么  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you wish for, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another piece of paper
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你许愿要什么呢  小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what did you wish for, little girl?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Front teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来顶新帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could use a new hat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要个新发型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a new hairstyle
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.55,0:08:17.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来杯水洗牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:17.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another glass of water for my teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.98,0:08:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.85,0:08:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming through
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out of the way
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you finished
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your wish?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的愿望是裤头村的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wish is that the people of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不要再去注意从这个这个傻子口中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will stop paying any attention to the inane drivel
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.28,0:08:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接连不断冒出来的傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is constantly streaming out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of this dunderhead's mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  也许圣诞老人会送我个词典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, maybe Santa will bring me a dictionary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我就能理解你刚说的话的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can understand what you just said
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我们已经召唤完圣诞老人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've got a lot to do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有很多事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now that we've summoned Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们必须要准备好迎接他的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must ready ourselves for his arrival
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(566,396)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.67,0:08:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精彩的节日马上就要浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's shaping up to be a wonderful holiday
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是那普通平凡的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not your normal average everyday
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有人砍了我珊瑚树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like someone felled my old coral tree
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为何要害我苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why'd you do this to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.86,0:09:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这世界好像充满爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The world feels like it's in loverly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.82,0:09:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点滚  不然我就要弄伤你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away before I harm you bodily
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.65,0:09:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个圣诞节就是我的第一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Christmas feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the very first Christmas to me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.37,0:09:27.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,购物装饰大搞特搞  雪大片大片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:27.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There'll be shopping, decorating and plenty of snow
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  是谁在槲寄生下面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, who's that under the mistletoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1196,880)}彩灯
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:36.72,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 圣诞习俗，在槲寄生下接吻 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.46,0:09:32.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:32.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.42,0:09:37.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这么晚了  我得开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:37.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you look at the time, I should go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.80,0:09:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家似乎都好像好兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People seem a little more brotherly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:47.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,660)}水果蛋糕
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有一点薄礼想要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a special something to you from me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.85,0:09:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连垃圾在圣诞节闻着都甜蜜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even all the trash, on Christmas it smells so sweetly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个圣诞节就是我的第一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Christmas feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the very first Christmas to me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知我事业不绝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that I'm busy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step outside
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有东西要让你发掘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've got something for you to see
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快把这玩意都拆绝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, take this stuff down immediately
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤栗得烧伤三度失了味觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chestnuts roasting and burns in the third degree
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.64,0:10:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今夜的一切都是那么欢悦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight things are as good as they seem to be
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树上的星终将标志美景无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A star on top will complete all the scenery
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.65,0:10:34.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个圣诞节就是我的第一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Christmas feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the very first Christmas to me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.65,0:10:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个圣诞节就是我的第一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Christmas feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the very first Christmas to me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is Squidward right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底究竟会不会有圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can there be a Christmas under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要走开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about time you got back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以继续讲完故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can finish me story
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.09,0:11:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝在送圣诞老人的最后一批信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, SpongeBob was sending
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the last of the letters to Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望他能看懂葡萄牙语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope he can read Portuguese
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  最后一封信送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the last letter
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.90,0:11:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥还没有写信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward hasn't written his letter yet
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.77,0:11:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你开头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll help you get started
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dear Santa Claus"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  算了吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  太正式了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, too formal
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hi, Santa"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.88,0:11:33.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诞哥好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:33.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Howdy, Claus"?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不给你幻想出来的东西写信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not writing a letter to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a figment of your imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等圣诞老人来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when Santa comes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只有你没礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll be the only one without a gift
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我到底得说多少遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, how many times do I have to say it?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不相信有圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只要写封信就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all you have to do is write a letter
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吃多大亏的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you got to lose?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会亏自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My self-respect
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亏理智
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My sanity
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亏午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别扫大家兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be a party pooper
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人就一大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus is a big phony
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝把你们都给耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob has got you all fooled
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让那些白痴熬一整夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those idiots are going to be up all night
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要睡个安稳觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I get a full night's sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight, tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight, tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱到圣诞老人来为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's sing till Santa gets here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight, tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight, tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.99,0:12:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight, tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.37,0:12:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Santa?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能随时会来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He should be here any minute
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming tonight, tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会今晚来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's coming
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.34,0:13:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老子受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough of this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你的一派谎言  童话先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the lies, Mr. Fairytale
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱换别处浪费时间去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go waste our time somewhere else
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的圣诞精神都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where's your Christmas spirit?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只是迟到了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just running late
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能他停下来吃宵夜去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He probably just stopped for a snack
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胖子会饿的  对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fat guys get hungry, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯神信不得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never trust a genie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经早上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning already?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.69,0:14:07.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到了拍圣诞照的大好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see a great Christmas photo op
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能移过来点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you move in a little?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say "Santa Claus"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.12,0:14:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的第一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our first Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.92,0:14:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个圣诞节就是第一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Christmas feels like the very first Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一个圣诞节就是这个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The first Christmas is this Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我的第一个圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause it feels like the first Christmas to me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个节日就是傻的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a stupid holiday
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还是要你收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still want you to have this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A present
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你做的  等圣诞老人来你就不会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it for you so you wouldn't feel left out when
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,落单了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa came
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.38,0:15:03.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:03.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他给我做了个礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He made me a present?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概率是个水母网
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's probably a jellyfish net
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者是个陈年蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or an old Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是他最爱的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his favorite underpants
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来好像一根竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it looks like a clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻起来也像一根竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It smells like one, too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用浮木手工制成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand-crafted out of driftwood
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,704)}章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面还写了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's even got my name on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,702)}按下
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.55,0:15:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我收到过的最棒的礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest gift I have ever gotten
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉就像个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel like a
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉就像个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel like a
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉就像个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel like a
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Big jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对那可怜的海绵宝宝都做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done to poor SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.65,0:16:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看我再也用不着这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I won't be needing this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The poor little guy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他想做的只是传播欢乐而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All he wanted was to spread a little joy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好把这些东西从章鱼哥家拆下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better get this stuff off of Squid's place
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.14,0:16:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人吗
