Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快现身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这上面  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up here, you dunce
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.24,0:16:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, little boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,San
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,San
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,San
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.30,0:17:18.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:18.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kid?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,San
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ta
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,San
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't do that again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会来  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd make it, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人  你的大圆肚子去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Santa, where's your big, round belly?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a result of
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在海底受到的水压比较大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,undersea pressure on my body
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你驯鹿哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's your reindeer
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你那会飞的机器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your flying machine?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把那些都借给复活节兔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I loaned them to the Easter bunny
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这鼻子怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what about that nose?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我知道你鼻子本来就很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you were supposed to have a big one
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是这也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that thing's gigantic
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你能给我的最好的礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest gift you could have given me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你把圣诞节带来裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing Christmas to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把圣诞节带来裤头村的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring Christmas to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴都完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有给我的礼物吗  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have a present for me, Santa?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.50,0:18:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧  我并不完全是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, I'm not really
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿礼物吧  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到了吧  他货真价实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, he is real
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他让我的圣诞愿望成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He made my Christmas wish come true
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不会让你失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He won't let you down
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, just a second
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, quickly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小女生喜欢啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do little girls like?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.94,0:18:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火柴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A book of matches
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.94,0:18:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是剃须用品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or a shaving kit?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我出生证明的复印件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A copy of my birth certificate?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边肯定会有可以给的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be something around here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.03,0:19:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  小女生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, little girl
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉好不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That almost felt good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.42,0:19:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人  我礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Santa, where's my present?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And mine?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what about me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看圣诞老人都给你们送来什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what Santa has for all you good people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使劲想  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think fast, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他们的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gifts for the people
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你碗土豆泥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bowl of mashed potatoes for you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好就想要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is just what I wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新发型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A new hairstyle
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手表
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wristwatch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当初怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把我东西全都送走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gave away all my stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就为了海绵宝宝不再伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just so SpongeBob wouldn't be sad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I insane?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门你也拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You might as well take the door
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只剩这玩意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all that's left
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你把他给错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you missed him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他刚来了  就像我说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was here, just like I said
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给了我们大家礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He gave us all presents
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他和蔼可亲  长了个大胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was jolly and he had a beard
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子也大  脸颊红润
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His nose was big and he had rosy cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别平易近人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was friendly and kind
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还特别圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Santa-ish
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他肚子虽然小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His belly was small
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他的大鼻子充满了圣诞的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but his nose was huge with Christmas joy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他人特好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was so nice
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  至少事都成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least it's over
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dear Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你的所有帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Thanks for all your help
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今年真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"You've been a real good boy this year
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,温暖的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warm regards
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.54,0:21:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm insane
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是圣诞岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's Christmas Island
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Presents Ahoy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.52,0:21:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A storm
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.48,0:21:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, yikes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把帆收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trim the sails
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吊起桅杆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoist the yardarms
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打开气象频道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn on The Weather Channel
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patchy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子们好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.95,0:21:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天哪  海绵宝宝让我可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, that SpongeBob makes me as jolly as a Roger
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们都喜欢海绵宝宝的圣诞故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you enjoyed SpongeBob's Christmas tale
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.96,0:22:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们圣诞节比沉没的宝藏还美好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I hope your Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is better than sunken treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂给我留了个小小的圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty left me a little Christmas present
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个槲寄生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ye old mistletoe
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.06,0:22:22.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道这是什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:22.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know what that means
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.98,0:22:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人该要来亲亲海盗派斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for somebody to kiss Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来啊  谁要来亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, who's it going to be?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.53,0:22:29.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:29.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给船长亲一口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kiss the Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.49,0:22:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给咱亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give us a kiss
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.99,0:22:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚  不亲你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.99,0:22:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲的不是你  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not you, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.12,0:22:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.91,0:22:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.58,0:22:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不要亲你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to kiss you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经说过这回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, we talked about this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.08,0:22:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.46,0:22:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲亲亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kissy kissy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.38,0:22:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  看来派斯现在非常忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like Patchy's pretty busy at the moment
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我来帮他说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'll say it for him--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.26,0:22:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.17,0:22:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,佳节愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and happy holidays
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:54.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1092,280)}佳节愉快
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.89,0:22:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我亲一口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a kiss
